--- Needed Packages

name    |    version    |    description    |
---------------------------------------------
gcc           10.2           GNU C compiler
libc          2.31           GNU C Library
make          4.3-3          GNU make utility to maintain groups of programs
autoconf      2.69           A GNU tool for automatically configuring source code
automake      1.16           A GNU tool for automatically creating Makefiles
binutils      2.35           A set of programs to assemble and manipulate binary and object files
pkg-config    0.29           Package compiler and linker metadata toolkit
ncurses       6.2            Curses emulation library
ncursesw      6.2            Curses emulation library (wide character support)
                             For example on Debian: apt-get install libncursesw5-dev
---------------------------------------------


--- Make sure charset is set to UTF-8
For correct display characters recommended use UTF-8 charset.
Run the 'locale' command


--- Spell
autoreconf -iv && ./configure && sudo make install


--- Launch and show your best result
typp


--- File Structure
/usr/local/bin/typp
/usr/local/share/typp/
/usr/local/share/typp/eng.typp
/usr/local/share/typp/rus.typp
/usr/local/man/man6/typp.6
